sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/Minio Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as External vLLM Server<br/>HTTP
    participant PyTorch as PyTorch Engine<br/>(in-process)

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2 - Model Initialization (startup)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        S3->>HF: KServe storage initializer<br/>downloads model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
        Note right of HF: Model loaded into<br/>GPU/CPU memory
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1 - Built-in Text Detection
    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP (Istio mTLS in mesh)<br/>Body: {"contents": [...], "detector_params": {...}}
        Note right of BuiltIn: Regex PII detection<br/>(email, CC, SSN, phone, IP)<br/>File-type validation<br/>(JSON, XML, YAML)<br/>Custom Python detectors
        BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score, ...}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,PyTorch: Flow 2 - HuggingFace ML Detection
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP (Istio mTLS in mesh)<br/>Body: {"contents": [...], "detector_params": {...}}
        HF->>PyTorch: Tokenize + inference<br/>(SeqClass / TokenClass / CausalLM)
        PyTorch-->>HF: Model predictions<br/>(logits / token labels)
        Note right of HF: Post-process:<br/>- SeqClass: label + score<br/>- TokenClass: span merging<br/>- CausalLM: safety verdict
        HF-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score, evidence_spans}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3 - LLM Judge Evaluation
    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
        Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>or POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP (Istio mTLS in mesh)
        Judge->>vLLM: OpenAI-compatible API call<br/>HTTP (configurable port)<br/>Auth: None
        vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response<br/>(verdict, score, reasoning)
        Judge-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Metrics Collection (continuous)
    rect rgb(248, 248, 248)
        Note right of BuiltIn: All detectors expose<br/>GET /metrics (Prometheus)<br/>GET /health (liveness)
    end
